name: Worship Me (Canceled)
blurb: "Worth every penny of your dollar if you enjoy action, a good story and last but not least something original and not copied for once."

rewards.reward: *Credit Given*\r\n\r\nThis pledge will reward you with your name being used in the credits of both game manual and in-game credits as a supportive backer of the project.
*Original Version*\r\n\r\nThis pledge will reward you with the game as it was meant to be. 100% originally unedited and uncensored.

*Japanese Version* \r\n\r\nThis pledge will reward you with the Japanese version of the game, uncensored and unedited. (note: Japanese version differs from the Original version. The two are not the same thing and will deliver a different challenge than the Original.)

*Wings of Alcador*\r\n\r\nThis pledge will reward you with exploring the contents of the land from above the clouds and then some. The "Wings of Alcador" will be yours to own and use whenever you want throughout the game. This special gift can also be used as a super strong attack against tough to beat bosses. Soar over all dangers and crush through barriers hiding valuable items. These wings will also allow you to unleash a powerful blast of electric energy. This item is not available in the original game.

*Survivalist Tools*\r\n\r\nThis pledge will reward you with the "Survivalist Tools." This wonderful piece of technology allows you to gain a boost in your vital and firepower supply. This content is not available in the original game.

*Velcon Ammunition Belt*\r\n\r\nThis pledge will reward you with the "Fireball Cannon Shockers." Power infused shackles allows you to fire fireballs. There's no limit to the amount of power you can unleash on enemies of many. Unlimited power means unlimited chances you'll outlast anything in your path. This content is not available in the original game.

*International Pack* This pledge will reward you with not only the Original Game but, you will also get the Japanese Version of the game as well. All together you receive both versions of the game as a complete package. Keep in mind that both games will be different from one another. The US Version of the game focus on the main protagonist while the Japanese Version will have two main protagonist.

*Exclusive Content*\r\n\r\nThis pledge will reward you with the "Wings of Alcador," "Survivalist Tools," "Velcon Ammunition Belt" and the "Fireball Cannon Shockers" all in one package. Backer will also receive behind the scenes look into the creation of the game and a limited edition "Worship Me" shirt with original artwork on front in back by the artist of the game. Plus a subtract Card which will benefit them in their purchase of another project from this team.
